M|Reca|When|
M|Reca|tx|1. **Identify the pattern.** Are er in one direction (over-confident 🔴 that proved 🟡) or random?
M|Reca|tx|2. **Isolate the bias tp.** Which bias is kh consistently over- or under-weighting in this domain?
M|Reca|3. *|recalibrate — the domain's threshold for 🔴 was set too lo.
M|Reca|4. *|**
M|Reca|tx|```
M|Reca|[dat|[what changed and why]
M|Reca|tx|```
M|Reca|tx|5. **Mark status as Recalibrating** until 5 new predictions are logged at the new threshold.
M|Reca|tx|---
